{
  "stem": "7722.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 24.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and we were over there in [GERMAN] in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in-- in '47.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In '47.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they decided all-- all the DP people with small children, they will take him to the DP camps in Germany on the American zone.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My-- so I had my daughter, my older daughter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was in-- she was, in that time, she was seven or eight years old.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- so they-- so they took us and they brought us to Germany to a place they called this Eschwege.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Eschwege at the Flugplatz means over there was-- they had over there planes during the war over there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were over there Flugplatz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not a airport.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The army was over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the air-- what do you call this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, a base.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had over there the base, and they had over there barracks all over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those barracks, we were about 3,000 [INAUDIBLE] DP camps, DP people over there in-- in Eschwege.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's by Castle.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By Castle.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- like I was in my youth, I was very active.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I saw what's going on in the world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I decided something has to be done to make the Jewish people free and let them to get their own [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was-- I was a revisionist, I was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I decided-- and I decided you can say I'm a chauvinist.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have to say the Jewish people are capable people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Jewish people are good people, not because I'm saying this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would-- there is-- there is bad people between us too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I wouldn't-- I wouldn't deny that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Just the majority people we brought up to respect everybody, to help, not just your own brothers and sisters, even your neighbors, not Jews.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
